AlphaGo also improved the quality and novelty of human play dramatically be=
yond the greats. In a March 2023 paper, Superhuman Artificial Intelligence =
Can Improve Human Decision Making [ https://substack.com/redirect/f98d952e-=
d09f-4bd9-a00a-5aec7fc202b0?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXe=
pKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ], a team led by Minkyu Shin analyzed 5.8 million move =
