What=E2=80=99s interesting to me is that, while AI has improved the level o=
f play in both chess and Go, it=E2=80=99s had a more significant impact on =
creativity in Go, because, according to ChatGPT, =E2=80=9CGo is a more comp=
lex game with a larger search space and more possibilities, which allows fo=
