6px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-left: 4px;"><strong>Doubling Down=
 on Our Minds. </strong><span>A renaissance in the exploration and enhancem=
ent of our minds&#8217; capabilities.&nbsp;</span></p></li></ul><p style=3D=
"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">T=
echnology alone won&#8217;t be enough. To make counterintuitive leaps requi=
